r />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0p41ZtpAh0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0p41ZtpAh0s&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTewdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9d97b4bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0p41ZtpAh0s</a><br />\n呢球古天奴就係直接參與進攻啦on9</blockquote><br />\n中間個件都唔叫直接參與進攻? 咁點先算係?<br />\n佢有走位入去而且係想射埋喎, 不過係俾人後上搶先一步射入啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旁證擺明係吹佢"},{"pid":"0dbf10e2f969ce2c9e86da92314adfe71cdca7eb","tid":135933,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心一問<br />\n我記得今年英超好似有條新例唔係話咩另一個進攻球員干擾位置就算冇掂波都可以計越位咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有干擾keeper判斷就係<br />\n呢球完全冇干擾到de gea</blockquote><br />\n衝哂出黎咁都叫無干擾到龍門<br />\n唔係要撞埋去先叫干擾下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nde gea望撚住邊撚到呀<br />\n行出嚟就干擾到呀盲撚</blockquote><br />\n係中間衝出黎都唔叫干擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有, 幾時旁證要判斷埋龍門對眼望邊?</blockquote><br />\n真接參與進攻呀撚樣<br />\n佢個人行出嚟就真接參與進攻呀on9仔<br />\n旁證係要判斷干擾到唔到龍門呀狗餅<br />\n呢球邊撚到干擾到呀死柒頭<br />\n黑撚完人仲可以咁撚串<br />\n做狗真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能球證覺得狗可以聞到有第二個人行咗出嚟咪吹囉"},{"pid":"7796b9f2081d68fe2ad82f852e14e488b9d4de15","tid":135933,"uid":12680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"妓學乜撚野人講黑哨<br />\n今季聯賽都唔知黑左幾多分<br />\n垃圾痢入唔到決賽就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8772e8ebc720c43e9e5a6289a59a52debd73c21f","tid":135933,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>妓學乜撚野人講黑哨<br />\n今季聯賽都唔知黑左幾多分<br />\n垃圾痢入唔到決賽就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\